# Policy Tracker — Next.js conventions

- Use **Next.js App Router** under `src/app/` (no `pages/`).
- Prefer **Server Components by default**; add `"use client"` only when needed (state, effects, browser APIs).
- Keep routes predictable:
  - UI: `src/app/**/page.tsx`
  - Layouts: `src/app/**/layout.tsx`
  - API: `src/app/api/**/route.ts`
- Keep code small and explicit; avoid clever abstractions early.
- Use `npm run lint` and `npm run typecheck` before shipping changes.

